    "jobDescription": "R&D Job Description : - 1. Core R&D Activities Formulation/product development, lab experimentation (Make, Measurements, Modelling/Simulations), process mapping, and gap analysis across Business Groups (Home Care, Personal Care, Beauty & Wellbeing, Foods & Refreshment). 2. Skillsets Required Analytical problem-solving, structured report/presentation writing, comfort with data and process mapping (manual vs. semi-automated vs. digital). Formulation science or engineering fundamentals are a plus depending on role. 3. Digital Tools & Platforms Working knowledge of Power BI for dashboarding, Excel/data analysis, and familiarity with ELN/LIMS or SAP-type enterprise systems. Exposure to Power Automate/Power Apps and Copilot Studio (Microsoft's low-code agent-building platform) is a plus  understanding basic AI agent architecture and data flow/management is valued but not mandatory. 4. AI & Simulation Awareness General understanding of how AI/ML is transforming R&D  predictive modelling and simulations (reducing physical trial-and-error), AI-powered formulation design, and self-driving/autonomous lab concepts  is a strong differentiator, even at a conceptual level. 5. General Traits Comfort working with cross-BG stakeholders in a fast-evolving digital transformation environment, quick learner of new tools, strong documentation skills for blueprint reports and executive decks.",
